OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly dry but a rather grey
OL,6,Fday overall with cloud only slowly
OL,7,Flifting and breaking. Some warm and
OL,8,Fbrighter spells are possible, mainly
OL,9,Fin the south. Winds easing.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FPatchy cloud in places that
OL,12,Fcan bring some spots of rain on higher
OL,13,Fground. Otherwise, dry for most with
OL,14,Flight winds. Feeling warm.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FCloudy in the north with
OL,17,Fbrighter spells in the south. As the
OL,18,Fday goes on, cloud will lift and break
OL,19,Finto the afternoon, leaving a bright
OL,20,Fevening. Feeling very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
